ws 2014<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後叫佢 restore 尋日個 backup （當 feb 2 requesting feb 1 backup) <br />\n佢一星期後覆我話(sat feb 9)話佢哋最舊得 feb 2 backup <br />\n中間催過幾次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://researchasahobby.com/full-list-eig-hosting-companies-brands/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresearchasahobby.com%2Ffull-list-eig-hosting-companies-brands%2F&d=vu6s8LH4hirWXswi0N35yv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=40f30bab\" target=\"_blank\">http://researchasahobby.com/full-list-eig-hosting-companies-brands/</a>"},{"pid":"3d3de75a21531011ba8de6205514cc0db00db691","tid":419514,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T17:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似平過晒嗰啲咩Godaddy，速度穩定性又高<br />\n<br />\n原生Ubuntu，自由度大咁多<br />\n<br />\n有冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識玩既就無得輸 唔識玩既就慢慢摸"},{"pid":"97b11af5c1cbe8b0ba6f7fc8969974592349500b","tid":419514,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似平過晒嗰啲咩Godaddy，速度穩定性又高<br />\n<br />\n原生Ubuntu，自由度大咁多<br />\n<br />\n有冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識玩既就無得輸 唔識玩既就慢慢摸</blockquote><br />\n我都零基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇住人地打一句我又打一句"},{"pid":"0151efc203ab2a79faa225f77924ff80e8646c6f","tid":419514,"uid":73231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似平過晒嗰啲咩Godaddy，速度穩定性又高<br />\n<br />\n原生Ubuntu，自由度大咁多<br />\n<br />\n有冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識玩既就無得輸 唔識玩既就慢慢摸</blockquote><br />\n我都零基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇住人地打一句我又打一句</blockquote><br />\n租個 managed VPS 跟人學吓先啦<img src=\"/assets